    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642333\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Render.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d9747486-359c-4e95-b49b-8dcafb0cea89\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1012 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506 1x\"></span><hr/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=468\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"666\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642330\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8a6cc1f9-9464-4aca-adc3-87cced6848e1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=936 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=468 1x\"></span><p /><p>Drop down a <em>volume</em> node to insert a VDB volume into a Solaris's scene and select the desired VDB file.  <br/>In the example above, a variety of cloud VDBs was used.  Smaller cloud VDBs were placed in and around the two open TeaPot flight cases and a large dense cloud was placed in the center of the scene.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=419\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"597\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642336\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b3cdda03-1280-4658-8fea-95600e46473f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1525&amp;height=711 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=419 1x\"></span><p /><p>A PxrVolume material was created and the density was controlled via a PxrPrimVar node <br/>Note : If you find your density is too dense, you can control it further by using a PxrExposure node and reducing the exposure to lessen the density of the volume.<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_PxrVolume.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_PxrVolume.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642339\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_PxrVolume.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5e16c741-e065-45d0-b896-4476a1fd97c5\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p /><hr/><p><br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642342\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"404bcb16-e793-4556-a261-ca2306ff6737\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>In the example above, a small layer of fog has been created to add a touch of air volumetrics to the scene.<br/><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=422\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"601\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642345\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist_Nodes.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"23a50ff0-dc5c-4be6-9ace-a8c6583141cb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1428&amp;height=671 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_floorMist_Nodes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433100832&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=422 1x\"></span><p /><p>To achieve this, a <em>sopcreate</em> node was inserted,ed and within that the following setup was created.  The density is controlled inside of the <em>volumevop</em> node <br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433101003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433101003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642348\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e8eb89ab-1379-45ca-be01-07f80078439d\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433101003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642318/RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433101003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642351\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Volumes_Nodes2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642318\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"823bde67-0bc5-4db8-9abc-8dac5b2d952e\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></p>"
    }
